Hazell currently lives in an apartment in Docklands.[1] She has been involved in two automobile accidents, the first of which was in 2005. In the course of a car crash Hazell hit her face on a door pillar, causing it to swell for a time. In February 2006, she smashed her Mini Cooper into a lamp post. She suffered no major injuries, but says she did fear for her life.[5]

In January 2006, Hazell made headlines when Chelsea F.C. football player Joe Cole was beaten up at a party held at her Grove Park house.[6] She spoke to The Sun in March, denying rumours surrounding the incident.[5]


[edit] Sex tape
In early January 2007, a sex tape of Hazell and ex-boyfriend Lloyd Miller was released on the internet.[7] The video explicitly shows her performing oral sex for several minutes and then sexual intercourse. The video was shot while the two were on holiday in Tenerife, Canary Islands, Spain during the previous year, on or about 30 May.[7]
